Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.81,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.81,Secondary,Dio,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:09.15,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:09.15,Secondary,Dio,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:29.25,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World is clearly much more powerful and precise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You have shown me enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.51,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Prepare to meet your end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:39.35,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The time has come for me to finally eradicate what little remains of the Joestar bloodline!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:40.60,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:45.44,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I shall finish you here and now\N with the mighty power of The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:49.02,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World! Time Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:01:59.47,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.40,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:18.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.70,Secondary,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:34.25,Title 3,title,0,0,0,,{\fad(985,555)\pos(132,890)}Episode 47: Dio's World Part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:40.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,At last, the Joestar bloodline will finally cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:44.39,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,To my greatest of enemies \Nwho dared to interfere with my destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.31,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...I bid you farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.03,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,He moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,He... Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.45,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Somehow his fingers moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.75,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.75,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.30,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It can't be... they're the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.97,Flashback,Jotaro,0,0,0,,So it's the same kind of Stand as Star Platinum. {copy pasted from 46}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:27.68,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,The World and Star Platinum are the same kind of Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:36.61,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This brat... Can he see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:40.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Or is it possible his hand moved subconsciously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.53,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,No more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.53,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:54.17,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Were you able to see me just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:00.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I asked if you could see me, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.05,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Who's to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.05,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I have no idea what the fuck you're talking about, Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.73,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Very well! It matters not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:20.78,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It makes no difference whether you can see me or not while time is stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:28.41,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,If you possess the power to move while time is stopped \Nas I can with The World, then show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:34.62,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,Indeed, I recall the moment six months ago\N when I first learned I could stop time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:43.72,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,To test the speed and power of my Stand,\N I ordered my servant to fire a shotgun at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.55,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,But as I prepared to catch the pellets...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:51.35,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,...in an instant, it appeared as though\N everything had stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.85,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,My first thought was that it was an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.23,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,Whether you're a trained boxer during a fight, \Nor someone faced with a harrowing situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.40,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,...you will experience each moment \Nduring that time as if it were several seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.40,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,...as I assumed was the case here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:10.58,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,However, The World was still able to move, \Nallowing it to easily avoid the suspended pellets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.54,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,What's more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.29,Thoughts,Dio,0,0,0,,...it was even able to grab them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.63,Flashback,Dio,0,0,0,,This isn't an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.25,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,Lord Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.88,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,I am certain you will master this ability to control time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:27.68,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,You must truly believe in your ability to stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.26,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,It must come as naturally as breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.35,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,Or as simply as snapping a pencil in half with your fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.31,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,You must reach the point where it becomes completely natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:40.36,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,Recognizing this fact is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:44.65,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,This power must become completely natural to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.95,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,You are the true emperor of this world, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:52.54,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,Controlling time must become completely natural to you!{THIS LINE NEEDS CHANGING IF 85 IS CHANGED}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:06:01.00,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Eventually, I felt the cogs of time\N and The World engage one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.30,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It felt as though a beautiful light had finally pierced the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.38,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Never had I experienced such a magnificent feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:13.01,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I, the mighty Dio, had finally surpassed\N every Stand and life form that ever existed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:17.44,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Although right now I can only stop time for five seconds, my power will continue to grow stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:23.69,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jotaro! Show me how powerful you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.45,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World! Stop Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.52,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,So you put magnets on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.02,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Did you do this while I was testing your power earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.90,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,They must have come from a wallet or pocket planner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.91,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You managed to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.78,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I mustn't take my eyes off you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.41,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:22.46,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Having to rely on such a simple trick proves to me that\N you really {\i1}are{\i0} incapable of moving while time is stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.00,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,All you have done is add mere seconds to what is left of your short existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.00,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.13,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Die, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.23,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:47.73,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,H-He... really... can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.99,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,If only for an instant, but he can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:53.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The magnets weren't to trick me into thinking he could move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:08:00.20,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,They were to trick me into thinking he couldn't,\N thus luring me closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:04.25,Flashback,Enya,0,0,0,,Controlling time must become completely natural to you!{THIS LINE NEEDS CHANGING IF 62 IS CHANGED}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:08.17,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Of all things... This Joestar descendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:12.68,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...had the gall to invade my world of stopped time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.19,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I could only move for an instant... Not long at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:31.65,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,But gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.45,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I only got one punch in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.42,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You. Woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.21,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Fetch me my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.76,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Do as I command!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:58.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Act as though you are a flight attendant, bringing it to me \Nas you would caviar and drink to a first-class passenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:12.36,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Guess if I don't go for your head, my attacks won't do shit to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:17.11,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You already regained your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:23.12,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,That hole in your gut completely closed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:34.34,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Your eyes followed me, which means you can see \Nevery single move I, the mighty Dio, attempt to make, Jotaro. {That punch through his gut wasn't enough proof? It was the eyes that did it?}{He's saying that even when Jotaro isn't stopping time like Dio can, he can still see what Dio is doing at all times.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.39,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.81,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Kakyoin gave you quite an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:45.89,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Because he figured out the secret of The World's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:52.65,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...it allowed you to figure out that you could move\N while time is stopped, and thus invade my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.82,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But now I'm intrigued...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.78,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,How long are you capable of moving\N within my world of stopped time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.41,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Two seconds? Three seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:11.42,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Or perhaps you can move for five seconds \Nand are pretending you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.01,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Won't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.76,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:21.30,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I could move longer if I practiced, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:25.64,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...for now, I can only move for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:30.90,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,If I were to guess... I would say you can only move for an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:41.20,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,However, since you managed to invade my world of stopped time,\N I will no longer underestimate you by coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.62,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,In spite of this, the advantage is still mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:53.59,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jotaro, your defeat will come regardless of how long you are capable of moving while time is stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.42,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:11:03.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The sight of these knives alone must have made you realize \Na fate far worse than Joseph's awaits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.06,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.14,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Where the fuck does he get these ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.98,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He's out of his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.65,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Escape is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.86,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.41,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Five seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:38.34,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Once time resumes, do you think your Star Platinum \Nwill be able to deflect all of my knives at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.01,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Four seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:47.43,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Bearing witness to your own demise \N must be truly terrifying, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.27,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Three seconds left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.02,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:01.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Only two more seconds! Is that the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:07.91,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This proves beyond a doubt \Nyou can move for no more than a instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.16,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,One more second...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.08,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.89,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But have another for good measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:42.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Honestly, I am quite relieved to be rid of you so swiftly, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:48.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I never foresaw you entering my world of stopped time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:57.29,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,To put it in perspective, despite how useful the automobile can be,\N it is rendered useless when the streets become overcrowded with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:05.18,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Which is why only I, the mighty Dio, should be able to stop time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.23,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.19,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Throwing all those knives at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.41,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I paid good money for this uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:33.70,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I stuffed my clothes with magazines \Njust in case he tried anything, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:39.79,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...I didn't expect him to hit me with a barrage of knives...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:46.47,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If I have any hope of getting out of this alive, I need to wait for my chance to strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:51.89,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If I don't find a way to smash his head in, he'll kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.48,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I must be careful now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The Joestar bloodline has proven itself rather fortuitous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,He may be acting dead to deceive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:14.50,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I must know that he is truly dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.00,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,So to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.25,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...I shall chop off his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.89,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This will finally put an end to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.10,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:49.40,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Burn in hell, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.54,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Burn in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:57.66,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:08.63,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World! Time has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.51,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,So, it was Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.23,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Resume time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.94,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,What a shame, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:34.28,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,With a bit more accuracy, and a little more force behind your blow, \Nyou could have severed my brain stem with your rapier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:39.83,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,B-Bastard! That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:43.38,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The mighty Dio never succumbs to sneak attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:51.59,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,And as for your little Joestar Egyptian tour group...  \NOnce I am done with you, it shall be completely wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:56.31,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,How'd it come to this? Now he's gonna kill Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:02.94,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It would have been best to play dead until\N I got my chance to smash his head in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:07.07,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...I need to act now if I want to keep Polnareff alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:12.61,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Still, there's no way Dio will enter Star Platinum's range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.66,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It will end just like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:19.20,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I need to make sure he doesn't realize I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:24.63,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,As long as he's unsure, my chance to strike will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.38,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,But talk about ironic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:36.18,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I tried as hard as I could to move while he stopped time, \Nand now I'm struggling to stay still while time is moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.39,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Farewell, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.27,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Jotaro, I heard that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:53.65,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You're alive... Or at least, you're regaining consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.62,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Don't move! Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.74,Main,Police,0,0,0,,We have guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:03.62,Main,Police,0,0,0,,Put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.17,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Excellent, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.68,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I would like you to shoot someone with that gun of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.22,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Use it on the man lying down over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.30,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Shoot his leg, torso, or wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Careful now. We can't have you miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:38.28,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Perhaps I only imagined Jotaro made a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.42,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You twisted motherfucker...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:51.34,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,At least now he's focused on me instead of Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.92,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He doesn't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:56.51,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He needs to know for sure that I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.97,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This is really fucked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.47,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The sound of his breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.69,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I cannot hear it. He stopped breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.77,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But what about his heartbeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.58,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This is insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:32.46,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,If I black out, I'm dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.84,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.18,Thoughts,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Dying while using my Stand to stop my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:48.73,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,He has no heartbeat. Surely he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.69,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Perhaps it really was my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:58.36,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But just to be sure, I shall chop his head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Is this agreeable, Jotaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.34,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.80,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.55,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Time Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:24.10,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.39,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I almost blacked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.52,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Even if you stop time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:33.36,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...I'll still smash your fucking head in, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.19,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,W-What? Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.11,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.16,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:50.46,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I finally smashed his head in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:55.79,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,But that Dio motherfucker survived for \None hundred years at the bottom of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.46,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He could still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:01.22,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I can't relax just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:10.39,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I shall kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:17.02,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,W-What is this? Impossible! M-My legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.36,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,My legs refuse to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.15,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I cannot stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:27.58,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This pain in my head... And this nauseous feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:33.33,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,How could this happen? \NThe mighty Dio, afflicted with sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:38.09,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Is the damage he did to my head preventing me from standing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:43.09,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Curses! I must act quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.06,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You'll be easier to track if I can smell the gasoline on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.77,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,I feel kinda bad kicking a guy while he's down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.19,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Nah, actually, I really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:21:01.03,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,My friends and a lot of innocent people died because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.54,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.92,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,That place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.80,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I must reach that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.97,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Time... Resume time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:42.15,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He put his head to the ground to listen for passing cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.24,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:44.99,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,He's not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:02.30,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,That place! That place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:04.30,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,As long as I reach it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:09.80,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Your hiding spot is taken. There's no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.48,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Give up already, Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.61,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.16,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:36.12,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora Ora Ora Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:37.87,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:46.63,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You fell for it, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:48.88,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This is my escape plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:52.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You've lost this battle of wits against the mighty Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:55.14,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Does this street look familiar to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:04.82,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,This street... I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:10.45,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:16.04,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,My escape plan was to take the blood of Joseph Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:23.46,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Damn you, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.51,Next Episode,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(960,730)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.51,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:31.59,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,This was a pretty great trip, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:34.68,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The blood of a Joestar is just what I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:37.22,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This is an amazing high!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:39.52,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Just one simple reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.10,0:23:41.52,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,You pissed me the fuck off.
