Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.36,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,952.999)}Seeking out...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:55.49,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...the slumbering legend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.32,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Scorching below us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:58.57,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...the shifting sands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:04.12,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Our destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:04.12,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...is awoken once again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:12.76,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,The tenacious blood that burns the silent flame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:16.84,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,The manifestations of the Gods that have been called forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:21.31,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...we will fearlessly pierce with our swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:25.85,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,As we march towards an uncertain destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:29.98,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,...the final battle draws nearer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:37.03,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,And the one to end it all will be Star Platinum!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:43.33,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Our tale has begun and our time runs short
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:49.88,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,To end it all the Crusaders must continue onwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:57.72,SC Opening 2 Eng,,0,0,0,,Let loose your fists on this blank last page!
